that rhymes.

13:26.588 --> 13:29.005
Izzy picked it.

13:29.005 --> 13:30.880
I forgot about
the list.

13:34.255 --> 13:35.880
You know,
you are the best

13:35.880 --> 13:39.671
I've ever seen
at whatever it is you do.

13:39.671 --> 13:42.671
Is it drawing...
buildings?

13:42.671 --> 13:44.296
-Mm-hmm.
-Yeah. Um...

13:44.296 --> 13:46.088
But this right now --
what you're doing now,

13:46.088 --> 13:47.921
the -- the whole
neighborhood thing?

13:47.921 --> 13:50.171
You don't want to treat this
like a corporation,

13:50.171 --> 13:52.130
like, uh, you're leaving
a body count

13:52.130 --> 13:55.588
on your ruthless climb
to the corner office.

13:55.588 --> 13:57.880
Lala is not the enemy.

13:57.880 --> 14:00.546
Did you know that she owns that
little hippie shop on the square

14:00.546 --> 14:02.921
with the soap and the candles
and the groovy hemp skirts?

14:02.921 --> 14:04.213
Oh,
of course she does.

14:04.213 --> 14:06.338
Okay.

14:06.338 --> 14:08.130
Just try not to
destroy anybody, okay?

14:08.130 --> 14:09.380
Okay.
Snacks are there.

14:09.380 --> 14:11.463
Uh...
I'm gonna grab my stuff.

14:11.463 --> 14:12.713
Thank you,
thank you.

14:12.713 --> 14:14.588
-Bye, girls!
-Bye!

14:14.588 --> 14:16.546
Have a good day!

14:16.546 --> 14:19.130
[ Door opens ]

14:19.130 --> 14:20.630
[ Door closes ]

14:20.630 --> 14:21.963
I miss you.

14:21.963 --> 14:24.505
Callie:
Poop! [ Laughs ]

14:24.505 --> 14:25.838
There we go.

14:25.838 --> 14:28.046
Callie, you can wipe her butt,
right?

14:28.046 --> 14:30.546
Wow, really feeling
the secondhand hate here.

14:30.546 --> 14:32.171
Oh, hear that?

14:32.171 --> 14:34.671
My new-girl card just
spontaneously burst into flames.

14:34.671 --> 14:37.255
Look, I got to find Alex.
I got to talk to him.

14:37.255 --> 14:40.463
Oh, good timing.

14:40.463 --> 14:43.546
-Hey, man, I --
-Hey, fuck you, "man."

14:43.546 --> 14:45.880
Who does that shit
in 2019 Portland?

14:45.880 --> 14:48.421
-Alex,
I said I was sorry. I --
-Dragging me into your
frat-bro scheme

14:48.421 --> 14:50.796
to get the girl or whatever --
I mean, that's bad enough.

14:50.796 --> 14:52.380
But egging my house --

14:52.380 --> 14:54.255
You -- You egged
his house?

14:54.255 --> 14:55.963
-When?
-Somebody egged
your house?

14:55.963 --> 14:57.505
[ Chuckles ]

14:57.505 --> 14:59.255
You scared the shit
out of my mom last night,

14:59.255 --> 15:00.921
you raging psychopath.

15:00.921 --> 15:03.630
At least
fucking own it.

15:03.630 --> 15:06.296
Look,
this is my problem.

15:06.296 --> 15:09.421
Don't follow me,
okay?

15:09.421 --> 15:11.171
Gabriel.

15:11.171 --> 15:13.630
We both know you didn't egg
any houses last night, okay?

15:13.630 --> 15:14.880
Why didn't you just
say something?

15:14.880 --> 15:16.588
Same reason you didn't.

15:16.588 --> 15:18.630
Because I would
get high-fives

15:18.630 --> 15:20.588
and --
and you wouldn't.

15:20.588 --> 15:23.755
I'm the asshole here.
I knew you were straight.

15:23.755 --> 15:26.130
I dared you to prove
you weren't. It's stupid.

15:26.130 --> 15:27.588
Look,
I'm not a puppet.

15:27.588 --> 15:29.421
Yeah,
but you're a teenage boy,

15:29.421 --> 15:31.796
and it's not, like,
that different.

15:31.796 --> 15:34.338
Instead of strings,
you have...

15:34.338 --> 15:35.921
you know.

15:35.921 --> 15:37.171
Look,
I'll figure something out.

15:37.171 --> 15:38.546
I just --
I don't want you to --

15:38.546 --> 15:41.671
"I don't give a damn
about my reputation."

15:41.671 --> 15:44.046
-Runaways.
-Yeah.

15:44.046 --> 15:47.046
[ Chuckles ]

15:48.588 --> 15:51.630
Look,
I'll fix this.

15:51.630 --> 15:57.880
♪♪

15:57.880 --> 16:03.838
♪ Now you want to love,
say you will ♪

16:03.838 --> 16:08.463
♪ Don't let go ♪

16:08.463 --> 16:10.255
[ Sighs ]

16:10.255 --> 16:13.005
This fucking sucks...

16:13.005 --> 16:15.046
mostly.

16:15.046 --> 16:17.463
[ Bottle cap clatters ]

16:17.463 --> 16:20.713
[ Cellphone rings ]

16:21.838 --> 16:24.255
Talk fast.

16:24.255 --> 16:26.171
I'm super busy
drinking alone in bed.

16:26.171 --> 16:27.505
It's 12:30.

16:27.505 --> 16:28.796
I'm making a point.

16:28.796 --> 16:30.046
That your life
is really sad?

16:30.046 --> 16:31.505
No.

16:31.505 --> 16:33.213
I'm on a mission
to remind Shaun

16:33.213 --> 16:34.880
that nothing matters
without me.

16:34.880 --> 16:36.380
And how's that going
so far?

16:36.380 --> 16:38.213
I'm getting worried
that I could rot here

16:38.213 --> 16:39.630
-and no one would notice.
-Okay, back to me.

16:39.630 --> 16:44.213
Anyway, um,
remember my boss, Nathan?

16:44.213 --> 16:45.921
-Test-drive boyfriend?
-Whatever.

16:45.921 --> 16:49.255
Um, so,
last night...

16:49.255 --> 16:51.463
we made some...

16:51.463 --> 16:53.838
not-so-good choices.

16:53.838 --> 16:55.380
You fucked him?

16:55.380 --> 16:57.130
-N--
-Whoa, you are terrible,

16:57.130 --> 16:59.380
and I actually, uh,
feel better already.

16:59.380 --> 17:01.880
No,
I didn't fuck him, okay?

17:01.880 --> 17:03.546
We agreed that
we were just friends,

17:03.546 --> 17:06.171
but then was this, like,
almost-kiss,

17:06.171 --> 17:08.546
and I'm freaking out
about it.

17:08.546 --> 17:10.338
Whatever, it's not about
the dude, anyway.

17:10.338 --> 17:12.630
-Explain.
-Everything you've said
or done

17:12.630 --> 17:14.213
in the past
couple of weeks

17:14.213 --> 17:16.588
screams that you are
nowhere near ready for the life

17:16.588 --> 17:17.963
that you're literally
signing up for,

17:17.963 --> 17:19.421
so you're acting out.

17:19.421 --> 17:20.796
You're, uh,
hoping someone else

17:20.796 --> 17:24.130
will make
the decision for you.

17:24.130 --> 17:26.463
-Still with me?
-Barely.

17:26.463 --> 17:27.588
Just sack up
and tell the Griswolds

17:27.588 --> 17:29.296
that you don't want to spend
the rest of your life

17:29.296 --> 17:30.630
in Hawthorne Heights

17:30.630 --> 17:32.671
and that you do want
to have your own babies,

17:32.671 --> 17:34.921
and maybe let, um,
what's-his-penis know

17:34.921 --> 17:36.838
that he's not the one
before he says --

17:36.838 --> 17:39.463
-I need you.
-Huh?

17:39.463 --> 17:40.796
I got to go.

17:40.796 --> 17:42.546
What?

17:46.171 --> 17:48.380
Gabriel got busted,
and Principal Morgan

17:48.380 --> 17:49.921
wants to talk
to him right now.

17:49.921 --> 17:51.755
-Why?
-Kid named Alex
accused him

17:51.755 --> 17:53.588
of egging his house
over a bad date,

17:53.588 --> 17:56.005
and there's a petition going
around calling it a hate crime

17:56.005 --> 17:59.171
and demanding
Gabriel's expulsion.

17:59.171 --> 18:00.713
Shit.

18:00.713 --> 18:02.421
Yeah...

18:02.421 --> 18:04.588
lots of that.

18:04.588 --> 18:11.755
♪♪

18:20.171 --> 18:22.171
What's all this?

18:22.171 --> 18:24.171
Oh, egg hair.

18:24.171 --> 18:25.755
Huh?

18:25.755 --> 18:27.213
Uh, somebody egged
your house.

18:27.213 --> 18:29.005
Mostly the door.

18:34.296 --> 18:37.130
So, you know Alex just
came out last summer, right?

18:37.130 --> 18:39.796
He doesn't have the tools
to deal with any of this.

18:39.796 --> 18:42.046
Oh, you think this is
for him?

18:42.046 --> 18:43.421
Are you sure?

18:43.421 --> 18:45.630
'Cause Hawthorne Heights
is so progressive.

18:45.630 --> 18:47.213
Oh, you know
what they say --

18:47.213 --> 18:49.880
hate hides
everywhere...

18:49.880 --> 18:53.130
-sometimes in
your own family.
-What is that
supposed to mean?

18:53.130 --> 18:55.421
Alex went out and hung out with
a kid from school last night.

18:55.421 --> 18:56.838
When he came home,
he was pissed off,

18:56.838 --> 18:58.880
but he didn't want
to talk about it.

18:58.880 --> 19:00.588
And?

19:00.588 --> 19:04.380
And obviously, I went through
his phone, saw the kid's name --

19:04.380 --> 19:06.046
Gabriel.

19:06.046 --> 19:08.171
Only one of those
at school.

19:08.171 --> 19:10.005
Same last name
as you.

19:13.046 --> 19:14.713
Izzy. Izzy.

19:14.713 --> 19:16.463
Hold up.

19:16.463 --> 19:17.796
Hold up!
Why?

19:17.796 --> 19:19.630
We can't let Gabriel
take the fall.

19:19.630 --> 19:21.046
Of course not,
but --

19:21.046 --> 19:22.421
but let's hold a beat
and think this through.

19:22.421 --> 19:23.671
There's nothing
to think about.

19:23.671 --> 19:26.505
Hey, we're gonna
lose our jobs.

19:26.505 --> 19:28.005
Well, then I'll tell them
it was just me.

19:28.005 --> 19:29.546
No!
That's not happening.

19:29.546 --> 19:33.338
Okay, look --
you confess, I confess.

19:33.338 --> 19:35.171
No. No.

19:35.171 --> 19:37.421
You have
way more to lose.

19:37.421 --> 19:39.796
You sure about that?

19:39.796 --> 19:41.713
Look, the three of you
just barely got that loan.

19:41.713 --> 19:43.630
And if
they re-verify,

19:43.630 --> 19:46.171
you are going to lose
the house.

19:46.171 --> 19:49.005
And I'm not just gonna
get fired, Iz...

19:49.005 --> 19:50.671
No one's gonna hire me.

19:50.671 --> 19:53.088
[ Sighs ]

19:53.088 --> 19:54.588
Why did I
drag you into this?

19:54.588 --> 19:57.713
You didn't drag me
into anything.

19:57.713 --> 19:59.963
I-I wanted
to be with you.

19:59.963 --> 20:03.130
-Izzy? Izzy!
Where the hell have you been?
-W-- I w-- I was, um...

20:03.130 --> 20:05.630
-We were -- We were
just discussing the...
-Oh, we were talking school.

20:05.630 --> 20:07.130
Okay,
I don't care.

20:07.130 --> 20:09.088
Um, Gabriel's innocent,
and I can prove it.

20:09.088 --> 20:12.505
-What? How?
-He was with me --
all night.

20:15.088 --> 20:16.713
He's trying to protect me,
but fuck that.

20:16.713 --> 20:19.796
I'm nobody's damsel.
Look at the time stamp.

20:19.796 --> 20:21.213
Nathan: Egging happened
around 2:00.

20:21.213 --> 20:22.713
Yeah, and we live
on the northeast side.

20:22.713 --> 20:25.088
So, he couldn't have
done it.

20:25.088 --> 20:26.338
No.

20:26.338 --> 20:29.046
Okay,
come with me.

20:29.046 --> 20:31.046
That's what I said.

20:31.046 --> 20:40.338
♪♪

20:40.338 --> 20:41.838
Dude,
what the fuck?

20:41.838 --> 20:43.546
I told you I didn't want
to talk to him.

20:43.546 --> 20:45.213
-Oh, oh, oh, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa!
Izzy: Watch it!

20:45.213 --> 20:48.963
Language, please.

20:48.963 --> 20:53.255
I just got off the phone
with your grandmother, Sasha.

20:53.255 --> 20:54.671
And she backed you up.

20:54.671 --> 20:58.546
You two are cleared.
You got this?

20:58.546 --> 21:00.546
-Yep, thank you, Principal
Morgan.
-Thanks, Principal
Morgan.

21:03.296 --> 21:05.588
I am so sorry.

21:05.588 --> 21:07.421
Still a dick move,
using you like that.

21:07.421 --> 21:08.671
Oh, yeah,
you're a massive choad,

21:08.671 --> 21:10.380
no doubt about that,
but...

21:10.380 --> 21:12.380
-Choad?
-...I don't know,
if I were straight,

21:12.380 --> 21:14.005
I'd probably fake gay
for her, too.

21:14.005 --> 21:18.088
Oh, my God.
That is so weird and flattering.

21:18.088 --> 21:20.546
I--
Will you please
be my gay best friend?

21:20.546 --> 21:23.046
Um, I'll put you
on the waiting list, I guess.

21:23.046 --> 21:25.130
It's like
we're not even here.

21:25.130 --> 21:26.380
Oh,
get used to it.

21:26.380 --> 21:28.171
We reverted
to being lamps

21:28.171 --> 21:29.796
and furniture
once the threat was gone, so...

21:29.796 --> 21:31.421
Mm.
Mm-hmm,
mm-hmm, mm-hmm.

21:31.421 --> 21:35.796
♪ Why don't you save me? ♪

21:35.796 --> 21:39.005
[ Door opens, closes ]

21:42.796 --> 21:47.171
♪ Whoa, my inner demons ♪

21:47.171 --> 21:50.963
♪ Yeah, we're on the same side ♪

21:50.963 --> 21:54.838
[ Scoffs ]
It's just you.

21:54.838 --> 21:57.505
Mm.

21:57.505 --> 21:59.671
Shaun hasn't realized
he can't live without you?

21:59.671 --> 22:01.421
I think
this thing backfired

22:01.421 --> 22:04.046
and actually proved
the exact opposite.

22:04.046 --> 22:05.546
Okay.

22:05.546 --> 22:07.630
Let's get you up,
walk you around a little bit,

22:07.630 --> 22:10.130
break up the blood clots,
air you out.

22:14.630 --> 22:16.171
Okay.

22:16.171 --> 22:18.755
So, once you're off the bed
for any other reason

22:18.755 --> 22:20.296
other than beer...

22:20.296 --> 22:21.755
-Unh, nah.
-It's over?

22:21.755 --> 22:24.630
No, you see, I never lose
at Bed Battles,

22:24.630 --> 22:27.421
and lucky for jou,
I'm not in the mood.

22:27.421 --> 22:28.755
-Okay? So...
-Ow! Ow!

22:28.755 --> 22:30.463
Mmf!

22:30.463 --> 22:31.921
Shouldn't you be fixing
the latest crisis you caused?

22:31.921 --> 22:33.171
Oh,
I already did.

22:33.171 --> 22:34.921
I'm still riding
the relief buzz.

22:34.921 --> 22:37.171
This is me
being here for you!

22:37.171 --> 22:41.463
I'm really struggling
to see it that way!

22:41.463 --> 22:44.255
I'm liberating you from a prison
of your own making!

22:44.255 --> 22:45.963
Bullshit!

22:45.963 --> 22:47.630
You're just annoying me
more aggressively than usual!

22:47.630 --> 22:50.588
-Oh! Yeah!
-No, no!

22:50.588 --> 22:52.005
-Yes!
-No!

22:52.005 --> 22:53.588
-No, no, no!
-Yes, yes!

22:53.588 --> 22:54.880
What's that?
What's that -- sorry?

22:54.880 --> 22:56.338
I can't hear you.
What'd you say?

22:56.338 --> 22:57.630
I'm better than you
at everything,

22:57.630 --> 22:59.338
including being smart
and pretty?

22:59.338 --> 23:00.671
Oh, my God, stop.

23:00.671 --> 23:04.005
You don't need to s--
Yes!

23:04.005 --> 23:07.463
The new Bed Battle champion
of the world -- me!

23:07.463 --> 23:09.505
[ Laughs ]

23:09.505 --> 23:11.963
You're absolutely certain
that this is you helping me?

23:11.963 --> 23:13.421
Yeah.

23:13.421 --> 23:15.046
And here's the payoff --
you'll never be alone,

23:15.046 --> 23:16.921
and you'll always be needed
'cause you've got me.

23:16.921 --> 23:20.463
Okay, stop threatening me,
and get off my bed!

23:20.463 --> 23:22.380
Uh, this is my bed now,
loser.

23:22.380 --> 23:25.463
Aah!

23:25.463 --> 23:30.713
♪♪

23:36.296 --> 23:43.963
♪♪

23:43.963 --> 23:46.005
[ Sighs ]

23:46.005 --> 23:50.671
♪♪

23:50.671 --> 23:56.296
Uh, hard fucking lessons,
tough love, baby doll.

23:56.296 --> 23:58.921
Stop looking at me like that!
You're gonna judge me now?

23:58.921 --> 24:00.213
Jesus Christ.

24:00.213 --> 24:01.463
Maybe I'm saving it
for our date!

24:01.463 --> 24:03.463
Did you think of that?

24:03.463 --> 24:05.546
Dick.

24:05.546 --> 24:08.380
♪♪

24:08.380 --> 24:10.963
So, yeah, that's when Sasha
saved us with those selfies.

24:10.963 --> 24:12.463
[ Sighs ]

24:12.463 --> 24:14.505
I'm so happy
to have that behind us.

24:14.505 --> 24:17.171
Nah, I wouldn't say
it's behind us just yet.

24:17.171 --> 24:18.838
-Well, I would.
-Yeah, that's true.

24:18.838 --> 24:20.338
Lala's door
didn't egg itself.

24:20.338 --> 24:21.880
No.

24:21.880 --> 24:23.713
I mean, I-I assume it's a kid,
right, because honestly,

24:23.713 --> 24:26.005
what adult would do something
so idiotic and immature?

24:26.005 --> 24:27.546
-Right.
-Mm-hmm.

24:27.546 --> 24:29.130
Certainly not someone
in this neighborhood, right?

24:29.130 --> 24:30.463
Oh, no.

24:30.463 --> 24:31.963
Talk about shitting
where you sleep.

24:31.963 --> 24:33.255
-It's vexing, isn't it?
-Mm-hmm.

24:33.255 --> 24:34.963
I know.
We'll probably never know.

24:34.963 --> 24:36.796
It's a mystery
for the ages.

24:36.796 --> 24:38.213
-Theories will abound.
-Mm.

24:38.213 --> 24:41.005
Podcasts will be produced,
probably.

24:41.005 --> 24:43.380
♪♪

24:43.380 --> 24:46.713
[ Doorbell rings ]

24:46.713 --> 24:49.463
Well, I wonder
who that could be.

24:49.463 --> 24:51.505
I don't know, honey.
Let's find out.

24:51.505 --> 24:53.588
Why are you guys
being weird?

24:53.588 --> 24:57.380
♪♪

24:57.380 --> 24:58.630
Oh, Iz!

24:58.630 --> 25:00.380
It's Lala,
and she brought a movie.

25:00.380 --> 25:02.963
Okay.
What kind of movie?

25:02.963 --> 25:05.005
A mash-up of my two
favorite genres --

25:05.005 --> 25:07.088
true crime
and found footage...

25:07.088 --> 25:10.338
from my neighbor's
security camera.

25:10.338 --> 25:11.963
I'll get the popcorn.

25:11.963 --> 25:14.796
♪ You haven't done ♪

25:14.796 --> 25:17.796
♪ You haven't done anything ♪

25:17.796 --> 25:22.421
♪ You haven't done
anything wrong ♪

25:22.421 --> 25:27.046
♪ Because you haven't
done anything ♪

25:27.046 --> 25:30.046
♪ I wonder what it feels like ♪

25:30.046 --> 25:33.046
♪ To not even have to try ♪

25:33.046 --> 25:36.088
♪ No action, no consequence ♪

25:36.088 --> 25:38.421
♪ So just go back
to your normal life ♪

25:38.421 --> 25:40.838
♪ Ahh-ahh-ahh-ahh ♪

25:40.838 --> 25:45.088
♪ I wonder what it's like ♪
